node.text: The #plantbased food industry is booming, but still often leaves something to be desired when it comes to delicious, crave-worthy flavor. Eating healthy and sustainably is important – but if plant-based food doesn’t taste amazing, it just won’t appeal to the masses. When I’m introducing people to vegan foods, taste is the ultimate driver of what makes it into my grocery cart or menu order, and that’s why I am incredibly excited to tell you about @motif_foodworks! They are re-inventing the rules using innovative science and ingredients – just look at this delicious animal-free burger! Check out the link in my bio to learn more! #ad
